additionalFields: [{"name": "SCOPE", "value": "Prepare base drawings through site survey, legal drawings and As-Constructed drawings (City or private utility), including BC One Call records.  All As-Constructed information provided by the City, obtained from COSMOS and private utilities is to be reviewed by the Consultant and transferred onto the base plan. The Consultant shall verify that all utility surface features shown on record drawings are visible on the road/ground surface, such as manholes and water valves. When considering as-built information, the original datum must be determined and any shift in datum must be accounted for.  Prepare a topographical survey extending to an appropriate distance on all sides of the project limits to an extent suitable for final design. The survey shall include the subject and surrounding areas to the full width of the road ROW."}]
